_sText:
This is a request for a smaller map of this one here - WMD REACTION
Smaller map, has only one Gen and space for 30 players max. Just to make it somewhat different and not just a completly shrunk down version of the map, the 3D skybox has gotten a major upgrade. what would look like lots of blocks could be taken as buildings in a city, up to you guys in the end lol. also tweaked a few other things, added a bit more light etc etc, but really just a smaller map. well, hope more than just the person who requested this can enjoy it, buyzones are in place if people want to steal it for fy or whatever :D
